attributionInfo.brokerName: eXp Realty of Southern California, Inc.

data.description: Great home minutes from Fallbrook Village but feels like you're in the quiet country.  Large usable 1.12-acre land with a HUGE shop and lots of room to build a ADU put in a pool or just enjoy the land. The two story 4-bedroom/3-bathroom home has new paint and flooring throughout and is at the end of private road.  The large deck overlooking the property is so peaceful and welcoming.  Make this amazing property HOME SWEET HOME!
